  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Il Segreto della Mente è sottile e invisibile, permettendo ai magi non solo di indagare i pensieri di coloro che li circondano, ma anche di influenzarli, avendo il dominio completo sulla volontà degli altri.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>SCIPLEMENTARI<br/></strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Quando scegli questo segreto, impari il @Compendium[historia-it.spells-it.3jBmsCuboaBsRGwA]{Friends} e @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cdrYKaFi98YWaBMw]{Vicious Mockery}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">cantrips, e quando ottengono un livello nel segreto si imparano gli incantesimi corrispondenti indicati nella seguente tabella:<br/></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips:</strong>@Compendium[historia-it.spells-it.3jBmsCuboaBsRGwA]{Amici}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cdrYKaFi98YWaBMw]{Vicious Mockery}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.eS7XnnApoxRxYXPs]{Charm Person}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.arzCrMRgcNiQuh43]{Command}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.3MYDjS6k9IYL0aTj]{Calm Emotions}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.ppWAAEul0QHtm4er]{Detect Thoughts}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.cg50KpBkBdPK6vPL]{Clairvoyance}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.GtGjNjPBgUHxGYAD]{Sending}<br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.ImlCJQwR1VL40Qem]{Arcane Eye}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.9hQXdMSmerkTsHDe]{Confusion}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5° livello:</strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.91Sw6vOIaO7U8DvM]{Dominate Person}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.fVbCxFRaORalHB20]</span><br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"/></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>MISTERI</strong> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"/>@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.KqYW295Mr9ZI3URu]{Founding Mystery: Telepathy}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.N7ze6bbx4SJMPJJw]{Major Mystery: Sharp Look}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.AyrHSbwKND2plFOj]{Greater Mystery: Evanescent Memories}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.LP7lJ6FfravT7shC]{Universal Mystery: Collective Mind}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGICO DEL SECRET</strong><br/></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">Quando raggiungi il terzo livello in questo Segreto, sei riuscito a modificare gli incantesimi che possono lanciare, adattandoli alle tue esigenze attuali e impara le seguenti opzioni metamagiche.</span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\"/></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.3459aAGgnOmf4yRd]{Metamagic: Subtle Spell}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">@Compendium[historia-it.profession-features-it.v7HWKi3xHaSwodoZ]{Metamagic: Incanto maggiore}</span></p>",
